docs {
  # Update List

  Updates an existing game list. Only the owner can update.
  All fields are optional — only non-null values are applied.

  ## Authentication

  Requires a valid JWT token in the `Authorization: Bearer` header.

  ## Path Parameters

  - **listId**: The UUID of the game list

  ## Request Body

  | Field | Type | Required | Description |
  |-------|------|----------|-------------|
  | title | String | No | New title |
  | description | String | No | New description |
  | isPrivate | Boolean | No | New visibility |

  ## Response (200 OK)

  Returns the updated list detail DTO.

  ## Error Responses

  - **401 Unauthorized**: Not authenticated
  - **403 Forbidden**: Not the list owner
  - **404 Not Found**: List does not exist
}
